
The software CCSM3 applies to create the mapping files is a 
software package called SCRIP and was developed at LANL.  
For more information on SCRIP, 
see http://climate.acl.lanl.gov/software/SCRIP .

CCSM3 uses version scrip1.4 and is found in the setup_tools
directories,  cpl/scrip1.4.

See the documentation and cpl/scripts/mk_remap.csh script for details.


